<donors class="MCRMetaLangText" heritable="false" notinherit="false"><donor xml:lang="en" inherited="0" form="plain">Sǝrnǝḥ (baptismal name Wäldä Krǝstos?), together with his relatives Wälättä Dawit, Wäldä Yoḥannǝs, Säbänä Giyorgis, is mentioned as the donor in the supplication formulas and Addition 1.&#13;
Names of other individuals are mentioned in the supplication formulas: Zä-Mänfäs Qǝddus (fols. 72ra, 76va), Wälättä Maryam (fols. 72ra, 123rb), Gäbrä Maryam (fols. 71va, 83va), Wäldä Śǝllase (fols. 102ra, 104ra).</donor>
